data.description: Welcome to your new move-in ready home! This charming residence features a single-story layout, inviting you into a spacious living area seamlessly connected to the kitchen and formal dining space, all adorned with elegant white cabinetry. The large backyard, complete with a privacy fence, provides ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Perfectly situated for commuters to Killeen/Temple/Belton or Austin, this home offers convenience alongside its comfort. Inside, you'll find wood-laminate flooring and tasteful tile accents, adding both warmth and style to the space. Located in the desirable Sonterra Community in Jarrell, residents gain access to the community pool, enhancing the lifestyle of leisure and enjoyment. The garage ensures plenty of storage space, while the pet-friendly environment welcomes your furry companions to enjoy the expansive backyard. With new paint, new carpet and modern touches throughout, this home effortlessly blends style and comfort.
